---
description: `/system/roadmap` data + git sync
globs:
  - frontend/data/roadmap.json
  - frontend/app/(app)/system/roadmap/**
  - frontend/scripts/sync-roadmap-git.mjs
  - docs/mvp/roadmap.md
---

- SoT: `frontend/data/roadmap.json` (bars/tracks/tiers/`gitPaths`). Narrative: `docs/mvp/roadmap.md`—update when scope/dates shift materially.
- After commits on **`dev`**, or when changing billing / `roadmap.md` / `roadmap.json`: from **`frontend/`** run `npm run roadmap:sync-git`, then `git add frontend/data/roadmap.json` if dirty; amend or small follow-up chore if JSON updated post-commit.
- Keep each bar’s `gitPaths` accurate. Run sync before pushing `dev` when roadmap-related paths changed. No auto-commit (`git-workflow.mdc`).
- Optional: `pre-commit` on `dev` running sync + `git add` for touched roadmap paths—document in README if adopted.
